---
description: Security and auth rules
globs:
  - "**/*.env*"
  - "**/auth/**"
  - "**/security/**"
  - "**/policy/**"
  - "**/middleware/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Do not expose secrets in code, tests, examples, or docs.
- No insecure defaults; use least privilege.
- Validate all external inputs.
- Log security-relevant actions (auth, policy decisions, data access).
- Every state-changing action must be designed for future auth middleware.
